      'As a psychologist specialising in neurodevelopment in Valencia, my first goal in the consulting room is to change that perspective: **ADHD and ASD are not diseases to "cure" — they are neurodivergences.** That is, your child\'s brain is simply "wired" differently from the majority (what we call the neurotypical brain). They perceive, feel and process the world with different rules.',
